{
  "texts": [
    "It contains 642 radiology images including 12 diseases and 39 organs of the whole body, with 14,028 QA pairs and 5232 medical knowledge triplets.PathVQA [78] is a pathology VQA dataset containing 32,799 QA pairs of eight categories, generated from 4,998 images.",
    "The majority of questions in PathVQA are open-ended, and the other half are \"yes/no\" questions.ROCO [80] is a multimodal image dataset, containing over 81K radiology images with several medical imaging modalities.",
    "It is constructed by retrieving all image-caption pairs from PMC.",
    "All images have corresponding captions, keywords extracted from the image caption, UMLS Concept Unique Identifiers and Semantic Type.MedICaT [81] is a dataset that encompasses medical figures, captions, subfigures and subcaptions, and inline references that enable the study of these figures in context.",
    "The dataset' s content is meticulously extracted from open-access articles available in PMC, ensuring figures and captions."
  ]
}